    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A distress call was received from space station RFA-1. The entire crew was urgently evacuated and sent to a nearby station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several employees are lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342880/extras/18c2d6abca696e032011884369364149.poster.avif?t=1731678514\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342880/extras/18c2d6abca696e032011884369364149.webm?t=1731678514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342880/extras/18c2d6abca696e032011884369364149.mp4?t=1731678514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a specialist in engineering department, you were sent to check the system data and equipment of the ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But a system failure at the station turned out to be work of an alien invasion, the entire station is captured by their robots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing remains but to enter into an unequal battle with uninvited guests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342880/extras/a363f3d979ee872a6c1117cbd0ea646d.poster.avif?t=1731678514\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342880/extras/a363f3d979ee872a6c1117cbd0ea646d.webm?t=1731678514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342880/extras/a363f3d979ee872a6c1117cbd0ea646d.mp4?t=1731678514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now your new task is to safe your life and leave the ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful graphics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spectacular fights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good optimization.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 types of weapons. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6-5 levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 types of robots. </p></li></ul>",
